    <li><%- t.privacy?.section_6_1 || '**Right to access (Art. 15 GDPR)** - Information about stored data' %></li>
    <li><%- t.privacy?.section_6_2 || '**Right to rectification (Art. 16 GDPR)** - Correction of incorrect data' %></li>
    <li><%- t.privacy?.section_6_3 || '**Right to erasure (Art. 17 GDPR)** - "Right to be forgotten"' %></li>
    <li><%- t.privacy?.section_6_4 || '**Right to restriction of processing (Art. 18 GDPR)**' %></li>
    <li><%- t.privacy?.section_6_5 || '**Right to data portability (Art. 20 GDPR)** - Data in structured format' %></li>
    <li><%- t.privacy?.section_6_6 || '**Right to object (Art. 21 GDPR)** - Object to processing' %></li>
    <li><%- t.privacy?.section_6_7 || '**Right to lodge a complaint** - With competent supervisory authority' %></li>
