    <li><%- t.privacy?.section_9_1 || '**Art. 6 para. 1 lit. a GDPR** - Consent by using the bot' %></li>
    <li><%- t.privacy?.section_9_2 || '**Art. 6 para. 1 lit. b GDPR** - Contract fulfillment (ticket service)' %></li>
